### Get all shipments
GET http://localhost:5000/api/shipment

### Get shipment by ID
GET http://localhost:5000/api/shipments/

### Create a new shipment
POST http://localhost:5000/api/shipment
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vehicleId": 1,
  "driverId": 1,
  "status": "Delivered",
  "departureDate": "2025-04-30T00:00:00",
  "expectedDeliveryDate": "2025-05-02T00:00:00",
  "orders": [1]
}

### Update a shipment
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/shipments/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vehicleId": 2,
  "driverId": 2,
  "status": "In Transit",
  "departureDate": "2025-05-01T00:00:00",
  "expectedDeliveryDate": "2025-05-03T00:00:00",
  "actualDeliveryDate": null,
  "orders": []
}

### Soft delete a shipment
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/shipments/1

### Create shipment order (assign order to shipment)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/shipments/create-shipment-order
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "shipmentId": 1,
  "orderId": 1
}
